Data Note: The following data is based on language in userâ€™s browser settings.

For "Language" (Column B), Google Analytics uses ISO code for language, followed by ISO code for country

ISO language code definitions can be found at https://www.loc.gov/standards/iso639-2/php/code_list.php. We suggest ignoring the country codes after the hyphen and consolidating languages across countries.

Eg: en (English), en-us (English, United States), en-gb (English, Great Britain), and all other "en-" strings can combined to find the total number of users with their browser set to English.
